Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:03:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きみだけをきみだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きでいたよ
